snippet.title: New World: Aeternum - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official announcement trailer for New World: Aeternum. 

Experience a thrilling open-world action RPG set on the supernatural island of Aeternum. As a shipwrecked explorer who washes ashore on the mysterious island, forge your destiny on an adventure filled with danger and opportunity. 

Coming to PlayStation 5, XBOX Series X|S and PC on October 15, 2024. Pre-order on PlayStation 5 and XBOX Series X|S to receive the Azoth Stalker Wolf Mount.

Pre-order on PlayStation 5: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10004947
Pre-order on XBOX Series X|S: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/New-World-Aeternum/9NPZJNVGHZ3P

Learn more about New World: Aeternum - https://bit.ly/3kTlRtV 
Sign up for the New World: Aeternum Newsletter - https://bit.ly/3YFYyoW

FOLLOW US ON SOCIAL
